{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第二日清晨，王一萍在府中设宴款待贺衔山与向衡飞。贺衔山表面赏石，实则暗中探听王一萍身世，套出其师龙灵飞已死、向衡飞乃魏灵飞传人之秘。向衡飞对贺衔山心生厌恶，拂袖而去，王一萍约其三日后再来。贺衔山趁机与王一萍亲近，引其往访名妓海萍。途中红旗帮暗中监视。在海萍处，王一萍与贺衔山饮酒甚欢，海萍与丫鬟小霞、妓女罗兰作陪。夜色渐深，王一萍渐觉销魂蚀骨，实则酒中被海萍下了药。红旗帮小铜锣设计利用海萍暗算二人，将其囚于破庙。贺衔山告知王一萍以重楼飞灵心法或可自解穴道。与此同时，向衡飞在市井中得知王一萍遭红旗帮暗算，念及师命与友情，决定前往搭救。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "向兄对这些像是毫无兴趣？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "贺兄不但文武双全，而且还是个风流才子呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "小弟一介俗夫，不但文武两途比不上阁下，就是这'风流'两字，在阁下面前也万万谈不上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "text": "这才是大丈夫行径。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "对于'酒'，小弟是万万不及两位，可是'酒'下面的一字么？哈——",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "饮酒而未对美人，实乃一大憾事。两位如有兴，小弟倒可做一识途老马。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "京城名妓，实有醉人之处，贺兄向居江南，恐怕还未领略过呢。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "走走！此间未竟之饮，等我们到那边再续上吧。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "text": "两位兄台有兴自去好了，小弟却不便奉陪。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "text": "兄台高义，小弟感激得很，只是先师遗命未了，小弟还是要来拜望的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "既然如此，小弟也不能勉强，三日之后，兄台再来便了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "只要小弟没有其他突生之变，定会给兄台一个满意的答复，此刻恕不远送了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "这穷小子是谁？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "此人乃先师生前一个大对头的弟子，他——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "兄台的武功，不是小弟瞎奉承，在江湖上已可算得上是顶尖高手。兄台的师父，想必也是位高人，小弟揣测许久，心里已猜中了八九分，兄台不妨说出来，小弟看看猜得对否？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "先师龙灵飞，过世已有十年了，兄台恐怕不会知道吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "原来兄台竟是'南灵'龙大侠的传人，龙老前辈隐迹江湖十年，武林中众说纷纭。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "却想不到他老人家已然亡故了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "兄台也知道先师的名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "'南灵'龙大侠一代人杰，江湖中谁不知道他老人家，谁不景仰他老人家？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "想不到他老人家竟尔仙去了，想必是得了什么不治之症吧？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "龙老前辈得的是什么重症，怎地突尔仙去了？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "先师是和他老人家的一个大对头交手时，各自中了对方一掌，竟然同时毙命了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "另一位可就是与他老人家在武林中齐名的'北灵'威震河朔魏灵飞吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "方才那位向兄，就是威震河朔的亲传弟子，他也要承继师命，来和小弟一较身手呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "这真叫做不自量力了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si",
      "speaker_name": "小厮",
      "text": "公子，车子已备好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "往事已矣，今日当欢，北国春迟，但探春须早，兄台和小弟且去做一探春客吧。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "此刻就去，未免太早了些吧。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "对于有些人说来，此刻确是太早了些，但对小弟说来嘛——",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "花贩",
      "text": "王公子，好久没看见您了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "花贩",
      "text": "今天您到哪儿去呀？敢情又是去找海萍姑娘吧？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "花贩",
      "text": "现在天还冷，花儿也不多，公子就将就些，拿几朵去吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "花贩",
      "text": "小的知道海萍姑娘挺喜欢这花儿的呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "好！好！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "闲人",
      "text": "孙老二，你小子倒是越来越花妙了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "闲人",
      "text": "我们的美娇姑娘想死您啦，您也不进来坐坐。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "看来兄台倒还是个'薄幸人'呢，惹得一个个大姑娘直想你，该罚，该罚。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "此地想必就是兄台的心上人海萍姑娘的香闺吧，我看还是兄台一人进去的好，否则的话，哈，哈，就是兄台不怪罪小弟，海萍姑娘也会骂小弟是个不识相的蠢材。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "兄台休要打趣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xia",
      "speaker_name": "小霞",
      "text": "哟，公子，您还记得我们呀，今个是哪一阵风把您可给吹来了？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "小霞，没多久不见，你又长高了些，变得更会说话了。嗯，也漂亮了不少。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xia",
      "speaker_name": "小霞",
      "text": "公子坏死了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "这地方真不坏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "你们姑娘在吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xia",
      "speaker_name": "小霞",
      "text": "怎么不在呀，我们姑娘整天都躲在屋里，想你呀，都快想病了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "海萍",
      "text": "谁想他呀！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "小红，快关上窗子，小心等会儿又着了凉。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "海萍",
      "text": "着凉就着凉，我死了也不要你管。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "好，我不管，你瞧你，又生的哪门子气。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xia",
      "speaker_name": "小霞",
      "text": "还不快进去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "请，请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "你看，又瘦了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xia",
      "speaker_name": "小霞",
      "text": "还说呢，我们姑娘都是想你想瘦的。哼，你们男人呀！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "海萍",
      "text": "您请坐呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "海萍",
      "text": "小霞，还不快泡茶来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "海萍",
      "text": "记得公子喝的是什么茶吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xia",
      "speaker_name": "小霞",
      "text": "记得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xia",
      "speaker_name": "小霞",
      "text": "我们姑娘百般为着你，你又有哪一件为着我们姑娘？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "这妮子越来越刁了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "海萍",
      "text": "你要嫌刁，就别来好了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "罗兰呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "是替他找。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "海萍",
      "text": "那不是来了吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_lan",
      "speaker_name": "罗兰",
      "text": "你才来呀，我等了你好几天了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_lan",
      "speaker_name": "罗兰",
      "text": "我作了一首诗，你看看好不好？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "海萍",
      "text": "你笑什么，不好是不是？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "海萍",
      "text": "那当然了，怎么比得上你这位才子。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "我也没说不好呀！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "劝君更进一杯酒，与君同消万古愁。王兄，再干一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "对，今朝有酒今朝醉。贺兄，我们今日要不醉无归才对。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "醉了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "是谁？是谁？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "旁边的人可是王兄？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "贺兄，这是什么地方？我怎么觉得浑身酥软，一丝力气也用不出来？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "我也不知道这是什么所在，看样子我们是被人施了暗算，点中酸软穴了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "点中了穴道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "王兄既是南灵龙大侠的传人，可曾修习过内家正宗的'重楼飞灵'之术？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "小弟十年来朝夕不断修习的，就是这'重楼飞灵'心法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "那就好办了，依小弟所觉，我们身受的点穴手法极为普通，想必非高手所为，王兄如曾习得此术，不妨以此心法一试，或许能自己解开穴道也未可知。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "text": "王兄穴道可曾解开？此刻已经有人来了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 455,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "这次真是大功一件，帮主若是知道了，再也不会骂我们是光吃不干的窝囊废了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "想不到江湖上鼎鼎大名的'翻花浪子'竟会落在我们这一批酒囊饭袋手上。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tong_luo",
      "speaker_name": "小铜锣",
      "text": "姓贺的，今天你可得认栽了吧。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tong_luo",
      "speaker_name": "小铜锣",
      "text": "姓贺的，你招摇撞骗，淫人妻女。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tong_luo",
      "speaker_name": "小铜锣",
      "text": "我们'红旗帮'虽然也是个见不得人的帮会，可是我们帮里上上下下，哪一个不恨你入骨？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tong_luo",
      "speaker_name": "小铜锣",
      "text": "今天你落在我们手上，好朋友，就认命了吧。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tong_luo",
      "speaker_name": "小铜锣",
      "text": "姓王的，平日我倒尊称你一声'公子'，是看得起你，可是你和这姓贺的一路，我们可有点不大看得起你了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tong_luo",
      "speaker_name": "小铜锣",
      "text": "今天没别的话说，也只好委屈委屈您啦。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tong_luo",
      "speaker_name": "小铜锣",
      "text": "哥儿们，我小铜锣提议，今天就在这里先把这姓贺的废了，免得日久天长，又生出别的毛病。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tong_luo",
      "speaker_name": "小铜锣",
      "text": "你呀，丢尽了你哥哥的人，这一次，可别再想你哥哥来救你了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "小铜锣，你做事可别太冒失了，舵主还没来，你少在这儿胡乱发表议论。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "我看小铜锣做事也太冒失了些，你看看把人家姓王的也给弄来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "人家是北京城里鼎鼎大名的公子，糊里糊涂把人家给绑了来，你们说该怎么办？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "舵主怎地还不来？他说他即刻就来的呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "我们舵主有名的精明强干，大约此刻又撞上了什么事，所以要来迟些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tong_luo",
      "speaker_name": "小铜锣",
      "text": "我知道他老人家绝对不会不来的，他老人家对这姓贺的也是恨之入骨——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 525,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "我们的这位舵主是不是当年……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "嘘，别提这事，等会儿给舵主听见了，可不是好玩的。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "你知道，我们舵主别的不忌讳，可就忌讳别人说及他以前的那档子事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "地痞",
      "text": "受气包，怎么好几天没看到你了？跑到哪里去窝起来了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 583,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "小铜锣跑来跑去，总算跑出了个结果来，听说那厮现在就在海萍那骚妞儿那里，喝得已有八九分了，眼看就要入彀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 591,
      "line_end": 591
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "听说陪着那厮的还是什么京城里有名的才子，叫做王一萍的呢！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 593,
      "line_end": 593
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "是呀，我也在奇怪，这姓王的怎么会和那厮搞在一块儿去了，看样子，姓王的这次恐怕也要跟着倒霉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "那厮得罪了'红旗帮'，也算是他活该倒霉了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 603,
      "line_end": 603
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "你可别弄错了，光凭我们'红旗帮'在北京城里的这一点势力，再加上玉面狐张舵主，可也未必斗得过人家呢。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 605,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "看样子这小铜锣还真有两下子——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 607,
      "line_end": 607
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "是呀，我听说那厮在大江南北很有点门道，武功也不错——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 609,
      "line_end": 609
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "他还好，他还有个哥哥你知道吗，可就更了不起啦。不过他哥哥和他不一样，人家可是江湖上响当当的人物。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 611,
      "line_end": 611
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "text": "他哥哥是否就是——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 617,
      "line_end": 617
    }
  ],
